    <!--
    Colors are set using #RRGGBB or #AARRGGBB where AA,RR,GG,BB are the hex
    conversions of decimal values 0-255.

    Common alpha values in hex:
        255 -> FF (100% opaque)
        204 -> CC ( 80% opaque)
        153 -> 99 ( 60% opaque)
        128 -> 80 ( 50% opaque)
        000 -> 00 (  0% opaque or 100% transparent)

    Use ColorPicker.com to pick #RRGGBB values, and prefix the AA values as
    needed.
